"wiki/International_Bank_Account_Number\">IBAN (International Bank Account "
"Number)</ulink></acronym> se trenutno ne koriste u &kappname;. Ova polja se "
"mogu ostaviti neispunjenim i mogu se popuniti kasnije; budući da su potrebni "
"samo za online bankarstvo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating an Account"
msgstr "Stvaranje računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:176
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "NOTE: You must have a file open before you can create a new account. If "
#| "you do not have an existing file, you will need to create a <link linkend="
#| "\"firsttime.3\">new file</link>."
msgid ""
"You must have a file open before you can create a new account. If you do not "
"have an existing file, you will need to <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile"
"\">create one</link>."
msgstr ""
"OPASKA: Morate imati otvorenu datoteku kako biste mogli kreirati novi račun. "
"Ukoliko nemate otvorenu datoteku, moracete napraviti <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.3\">novu datoteku</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To create a new account, you can either select "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Account</guimenu><guimenuitem>New account...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu or choose the "
#| "<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"newacct.png"
#| "\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject><textobject> <phrase>New</phrase></"
#| "textobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> icon from the toolbar."
msgid ""
"To create a new account, you can either select the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu><guimenuitem>New account...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item or choose the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"newacct.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> new account "
"icon from the toolbar. You can also create an account from the Accounts "
"View; click the Accounts icon in the View Selector and then right-click the "
"Asset or Liability tree icon and select <guimenuitem>New account...</"
"guimenuitem> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Da biste napravili novi račun, možete odabrati ili "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Account</guimenu><guimenuitem>New account...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz menija ili "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"newacct.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject><textobject> <phrase>New</phrase></"
"textobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> ikonu iz toolbar-a."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Institution (Bank) name"
msgstr "Ime institucije(banke)"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:195
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Parent Account</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - institution</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nadređeni račun</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - institution</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The first step involves selecting an institution for the account. If this "
#| "is an account for an institution you have already created, you can select "
#| "the institution from the dropdown list. If you want to create a new "
#| "institution, click on the <guibutton>New Institution</guibutton> button. "
#| "This will bring up the New Institution Dialog, as described in the "
#| "previous section. If this is not a bank account, or if you do not want to "
#| "use online banking, you do not need to specify an institution."
msgid ""
"The first step involves selecting an institution for the account. If this is "
"an account for an institution you have already created, you can select the "
"institution from the dropdown list. If you want to create a new institution, "
"click <guibutton>New Institution</guibutton>. This will bring up the New "
"Institution Dialog, as described in the previous section. If this is not a "
"bank account, or if you do not want to use online banking, you do not need "
"to specify an institution."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak uključuje odabir institucije za račun. Ukoliko je račun vezan za "
"insituciju koju ste već kreirali, možete je izabrati iz opadajuće liste. "
"Ukoliko želite da napravite novu instituciju, kliknite na <guibutton>New "
"Institution</guibutton> dugme. Ovo će otvoriti New Institution dijalog, kao "
"što je prethodno opisano. Ukoliko ne želite da napravite bankovni račun ili "
"ukoliko ne želite da koristite online bankarstvo, onda ne morate "
"specificirati instituciju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Account Number and the <acronym><ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/"
#| "wiki/International_Bank_Account_Number\">IBAN (International Bank Account "
#| "Number)</ulink></acronym> are not currently used by &kappname;. These "
#| "fields may be left blank and filled in at a later time; they are only "
#| "required for online banking."
msgid ""
"The Account Number and the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"International_Bank_Account_Number\"> <acronym>IBAN</acronym> (International "
"Bank Account Number)</ulink> are not required by &kmymoney;. These fields "
"may be left blank and filled in at a later time. The account number may be "
"used for <link linkend=\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect\">online banking</"
"link> and to assure data imports use the right account. The <acronym>IBAN</"
"acronym> may be used by the KBanking plugin."
msgstr ""
"Account Number(broj računa) i <acronym><ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/International_Bank_Account_Number\">IBAN (International Bank Account "
"Number)</ulink></acronym> se trenutno ne koriste u &kappname;. Ova polja se "
"mogu ostaviti neispunjenim i mogu se popuniti kasnije; budući da su potrebni "
"samo za online bankarstvo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:227 details-accounts.docbook:376
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "To proceed to the next step click on <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgid "To proceed to the next step click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Da biste nastavili sa sljedećim korakom, kliknite na <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:234
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Parent Account</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - account details</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nadređeni račun</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - account details</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, enter a name for the account. This name will be used to identify it."
msgstr "Prvo unesite ime računa. Ovo ime će se koristiti za identifikaciju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, select the type of account from one of the types available from the "
"dropdown list. Different account types are handled differently within "
"&kmymoney;, so it is important to choose the correct type when creating the "
"account. Also, different types of accounts require different setup "
"information, and may display different pages in the new account setup wizard "
"to collect that information."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking"
msgstr "Provjeravam"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:261
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A normal checking account, the type you get with any bank or credit union."
msgid ""
"A normal checking account, such as you get with any bank or credit union."
msgstr "Uobičajeni tekući račun, kakav dobijate i u banci."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Savings"
msgstr "Usteđevina"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:270
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A normal savings account, the type you get with any bank or credit union."
msgid ""
"A normal savings account, such as you get with any bank or credit union."
msgstr "Uobičajeni štedni račun, koji također možete otvoriti u banci."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credit Card"
msgstr "Kreditna kartica"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "An account to represent your credit card."
msgstr "Račun koji predstavlja vaša kreditnu karticu."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cash"
msgstr "Gotovina"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A general purpose account, typically used for accounts not held at a bank, "
"such as the cash in your wallet."
msgstr ""
"Opštenamjenski račun, koji se tipično koristi kao račun koji nije otvoren u "
"banci, npr. gotovina koju nosite sa sobom."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan"
msgstr "Zajam"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:298
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "An account to manage a loan for money either borrowed or lent. With a "
#| "Loan account &kappname; automatically calculates interest payments to "
#| "help you track the remaining principal on the loan. Loans with no "
#| "interest might use the plain Asset or Liability type below, depending on "
#| "whether the money is lent or borrowed."
msgid ""
"An account to manage a loan for money either borrowed or lent. With a Loan "
"account, &kmymoney; automatically calculates interest payments to help you "
"track the remaining principal on the loan. Loans with no interest should use "
"the plain Asset or Liability type below, depending on whether the money is "
"lent or borrowed. A <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">schedule</link> can "
"be created to manage ongoing payments."
msgstr ""
"Račun koji predstavlja novac koji je ili posuđen od nekog ili posuđen "
"nekome. Sa Loan računom &kappname; automatski računa i plaćanje kamate kako "
"bi lakše pratili koliko vam je novca u zadaom momentu preostalo da "
"isplatite. Loan računi bez kamata se mogu napraviti i kao Asset ili "
"Liability računi spomenuti prije, u ovisnosti da li je novac posuđen nekome "
"ili posuđen od nekog."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investment"
msgstr "Investicija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:312
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "An account to manage an investment such as stocks or investment funds."
msgid ""
"An account to manage an investment such as stocks, bonds, or mutual funds."
msgstr ""
"Račun koji upravlja investicijama kao što su dionice ili investiocini "
"fondovi."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Asset"
msgstr "Sredstvo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:321
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "An account to manage an asset that does not fit in one of the above types."
msgid ""
"An account to manage an asset that does not fit in one of the above types. "
"For example, this can be used to track the value of a vehicle."
msgstr ""
"Račun koji upravlja sredstvima koja ne pripadaju dosad navedenim tipovima "
"računa."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Liability"
msgstr "Obaveza"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:331
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "An account to manage a liability such as money you borrowed or a future "
#| "expense. If interest needs to be calculated, you might be better using "
#| "the Loan type above."
msgid ""
"An account to manage a money you owe or a future expense that does not fit "
"in one of the above types. This is most commonly used for loans with no "
"interest. If interest needs to be calculated, you should use the Loan type "
"above."
msgstr ""
"Račun koji upravlja odgovornostima kao što su novac koji ste posudili od "
"nekoga ili neki trošak u budućnosti. Ukoliko kamate trebaju biti izračunate, "
"preporučeno je da se koristi Loan tip računa."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Equity"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Accounts of this type are used for Opening Balance Transactions in other "
"accounts. &kmymoney; automatically creates one account of this type and it "
"is rarely necessary to create another."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:352
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Select the currency to be used for the account from the dropdown list."
msgid ""
"Select the currency to be used for the account from the dropdown list. The "
"default is the currency chosen when the data file was created."
msgstr "Izaberite valutu koja će se koristiti za račun iz opadajuće liste."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the date the account was opened or select it from the calendar using "
"the icon to the right. You will not be able to enter any transaction with a "
"date earlier than the account opening date, but you can change this date "
"later, if necessary."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:364
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Enter the opening balance for the account. If this is an existing bank "
#| "account this information can be found on your statement. If it is a new "
#| "account, the opening balance can be left at zero."
msgid ""
"Enter the opening balance for the account. If this is an existing bank "
"account, this information can be found on your statement. If it is a new "
"account, the opening balance can be left at zero."
msgstr ""
"Unesite početno stanje računa. Ukoliko je ovo postojeći račun iz banke, ovu "
"informaciju možete naći na izvodu. Ukoliko je ovo novi račun, početno stanje "
"se može ostaviti na nuli."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:370
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Selecting the <emphasis>Preferred Account</emphasis> check box will allow "
