#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investment Accounts"
msgstr "Investicioni računi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &kmymoney;, Investment accounts contain only equities (stocks, bonds, "
"&etc;) but do not contain cash. (This is why you cannot specify a Opening "
"balance for an Investment account.) If a transaction in an Investment "
"account requires or generates cash (such as to buy or sell stock,) a "
"Brokerage account is used for the cash. Brokerage accounts are described "
"further in the chapter on <link linkend=\"details.investments\">Investments</"
"link>. When you create a new Investment account, after entering the basic "
"information, and clicking <guibutton>Next</guibutton>, you have the option "
"to create an associated Brokerage account."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There have been many requests to let Investment accounts also hold cash, and "
"this will likely be possible in a future version of &kmymoney;, along with "
"other things not currently possible. However, this will involve a "
"significant effort, and is not expected in the near future."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:431
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Parent Account</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - investment</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nadređeni račun</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - investment</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is generally best to create the Brokerage account here, which will be "
"given the same name as the Investment account, with \"(Brokerage)\" "
"appended. Currently it is not possible to specify the opening date or "
"balance for the Brokerage account at this point; you may do by editing the "
"account details after the account has been created."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan Accounts"
msgstr "Računi zajmova"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:452
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Loan accounts are special accounts used to help you manage Loans with "
#| "interest and scheduled repayments. By providing &kappname; with "
#| "information about the loan, &kappname; can help you track interest "
#| "payments and the remaining principal of the loan."
msgid ""
"Loan accounts have special features to help you manage Loans with interest "
"and scheduled repayments. By providing &kmymoney; with information about the "
"loan, &kmymoney; can help you track interest payments and the remaining "
"principal of the loan."
msgstr ""
"Računi zajmova su posebni računi koji vam pomažu da upravljate zajmovima sa "
"kamatom i isplaniranim isplatama. Dajući &kappname; sve informacije o zajmu, "
"&kappname; vam može pomoći da pratite kamate isplate i ostatak duga."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:460
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Parent Account</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - loan details</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nadređeni račun</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - loan details</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "On the Details page you enter the general information about the loan."
msgstr "Na stranici detalja unosite sve detaljne informacije o zajmu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:475
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "First, select whether you are borrowing or lending money. If you are "
#| "borrowing money the loan will be listed in Accounts under Liabilities. If "
#| "you are lending money the loan will be listed under Assets."
msgid ""
"First, select whether you are borrowing or lending money. If you are "
"borrowing money the loan will be a Liability account. If you are lending "
"money the loan will be an Asset account."
msgstr ""
"Prvo odaberite da li posuđujete novac od nekoga ili ga vi posuđujete nekom. "
"Ukoliko vi posuđujete novac od nekog, zajam će biti napravljen kao Liability "
"račun. Ukoliko vi posuđujete novac nekome, zajam će biti napravljen kao "
"Asset račun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:481
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Next, select the payee or payer of the loan. As always, if the name "
#| "doesn't yet exist in the Payees list, enter it here and &kappname; will "
#| "create it for you."
msgid ""
"Next, select the payee or payer of the loan. As always, if the name doesn't "
"yet exist in the Payees list, enter it here and &kmymoney; will create it "
"for you."
msgstr ""
"Zatim odredite osobu koja daje zajam ili koja je dužna da ga vrati. Kao i "
"uvijek, ukoliko ime još uvijek ne postoji na listi osoba, samo ga unesite i "
"&kappname; će ga napraviti za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:486
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The next three items are for handling Loans on which you've already made "
#| "payments. If you select Yes in the \"Have you made/received any payments "
#| "yet?\" item you can then select whether you want to record all payments "
#| "or just those from the beginning of the current year. If you want to "
#| "record from the beginning of the current year, you are than asked to "
#| "input the current balance."
msgid ""
"The next three items are for handling Loans on which payments have already "
"been made, If you select <guibutton>Yes</guibutton> in the <guilabel>Did you "
"make/receive any payments yet?</guilabel> dropdown, you can then select "
"whether you want to record all payments or just those from the beginning of "
"the current year. If you want to record from the beginning of the current "
"year, you are than asked to input the balance at the beginning of this year."
msgstr ""
"Sljedeće tri stavke se odnose na zajmove za koje ste već izvršili neke "
"uplate. Ukoliko odaberete \"Da\" u \"Da li ste već načinili neku isplatu ili "
"primili određeni novac?\", možete odabrati da li želite da se sve isplate/"
"uplate bilježe ili samo one s početka godine. Ukoliko želite da bilježite "
"uplate/isplate od početka trenutne godine, bićete upitani da unesete "
"trenutno stanje računa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:495
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Then, select how often payments will be made and how often interest is "
#| "compounded. Compounding is where the interest is added to the amount owed "
#| "on the loan so that when the interest is next calculated there will be "
#| "more interest paid on the interest. It's common for interest to be "
#| "compounded at the same frequency that payments are made."
msgid ""
"Next, select how often payments will be made and how often interest is "
"compounded. Compounding is where the interest is added to the amount owed on "
"the loan so that when the interest is next calculated there will be more "
"interest paid on the interest. It's common for interest to be compounded at "
"the same frequency that payments are made."
msgstr ""
"Zatim odaberite koliko često će uplate biti izvršene i koliko često će se "
"vrijednost kamate mijenjati. Dolazi do promjene kamate pošto će se prilikom "
"prvog računanja vrijednost duga povećati, pa će se sljedeći put obračunati "
"kamata i na tu dodanu vrijednost. Uobičajeno je da se stopa kredita mijenja "
"simultano sa vršenjem uplate."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:503
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Next, enter the date the first recorded payment will be made."
msgid "Next, enter the date the first payment to be recorded."
msgstr "Zatim unesite datum prve uplate koja će biti zabilježena."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:507
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Finally, enter information about how the interest rate varies. If the "
#| "loan is fixed-rate there is nothing to do. If the rate varies, select "
#| "Variable in \"Type of interest rate\" and then enter the interval between "
#| "interest rate changes and the date the first change of interest rate is "
#| "due: &kappname; will ask you to update the interest rate when that date "
#| "arrives."
msgid ""
"Finally, enter information about how the interest rate varies. If the loan "
"is fixed-rate there is nothing to do. If the rate varies, select Variable in "
"<guilabel>Type of interest rate</guilabel> and then enter the interval "
"between interest rate changes and the date the first change of interest rate "
"is due: &kmymoney; will ask you to update the interest rate when that date "
"arrives. Click <guibutton>Next</guibutton> to continue."
msgstr ""
"Na kraju unesite informaciju o tome kako će se stopa kamate mijenjati. "
"Ukoliko je zajam fiksiran onda ne morate ništa dodati. Ukoliko će vrijednost "
"kamate varirati, onda odaberite Variable(promjenljivo) u \"Type of interest "
"rate\"(vrsta kamate) i onda unesite interval između kojeg će se stopa kamate "
"mijenjati i datum kada će doći do prve promjene: &kappname; će od vas "
"tražiti da promjenite stopu kamate kada dođe taj datum."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:517
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Parent Account</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - loan payments</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nadređeni račun</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - loan payments</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Payments page is where you enter the payment and interest values for the "
"loan."
msgstr ""
"Payments(plaćanja) stranica predstavlja mjesto na kojem unosite uplate i "
"stopu kamate za zajam."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, select whether the interest rate is calculated when the payment is "
"received or when it becomes due. If you don't know, leave it on the default "
"value."
msgstr ""
"Prvo odaberite da li se kamata računa kada se primi uplata ili kada se "
"dosegne rok. Ukoliko niste sigurni, ostavite na predefinisanu vrijednost."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next, enter the following values:"
msgstr "Zatim unesite sljedeće vrijednosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan amount"
msgstr "Iznos kredita"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of the loan."
msgstr "Iznos kredita."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interest rate"
msgstr "Kamatnu stopu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The annual percentage interest rate of the loan. This must be a positive "
"number. If there is no interest, then the loan should be created as an Asset "
"or Liability account."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Term"
msgstr "Rok"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The length of the loan. Enter a number and select either Months or Years."
msgstr ""
"Dužinu kredita. Unesite broj i odaberite da li on predstavlja mjesece ili "
"godine."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payment (principal and interest)"
msgstr "Plaćanje (glavnica i kamata)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:572
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The amount paid for each loan payment. This is the total of the principal "
#| "and interest paid with each payment."
msgid ""
"The amount of each loan payment. This is the total of the principal and "
"interest paid with each payment."
msgstr ""
"Iznos plaćen za svaku uplatu kredita. ovo je ukupna količina glavnice i "
"kamate isplaćena svakom isplatom."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balloon payment"
msgstr "Balonsko plaćanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional final payment made at the end of the term to pay off the "
"remaining principal of the loan. For a repayment loan this is often zero. "
"For an interest-only loan this will be the same as the loan amount."
msgstr ""
"Dodatna završna isplata na kraju roka kojom se isplaćuje ostatak glavnice "
"kredita. Ukoliko se radi o kreditu vezanom za otplatu ova vrijednost će "
"većinom biti nula. Za kredite vezana za isplatu, ova će vrijednost biti ista "
"kao iznos kredita."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:591
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Finally, use the <guibutton>Calculate</guibutton> button to check the "
#| "values you have entered. You must have entered either all or all but one "
#| "of the values listed above. If you omit two or more values the button is "
#| "disabled because it is not possible to check that the entered values are "
#| "consistent: in that case you will not be able to use the Loan account "
#| "facility in &kappname; and will instead have to use a Liability or Asset "
#| "account to track the loan manually."
msgid ""
"Finally, use the <guibutton>Calculate</guibutton> button to check the values "
"you have entered. You must have entered either all or all but one of the "
"values listed above. If you omit two or more values the button is disabled "
"because it is not possible to check that the entered values are consistent: "
"in that case you will not be able to use the Loan account facility in "
"&kmymoney; and will instead have to use a Liability or Asset account to "
"track the loan manually."
msgstr ""
"Koristite <guibutton>Izračunaj</guibutton> dugme da biste provjerili "
"vrijednosti koje ste unijeli. Morali ste unijeti ili sve ili sve osim jedne "
"vrijednosti. Ukoliko zaboravite unijeti dvije ili više vrijednosti, ovo "
"dugme neće biti omogućeno jer je nemoguća provjera konzistentnosti svih "
"vrijednosti, ukoliko one nisu unesene. U tom slučaju nećete moći koristiti "
"opcije Loan računa u &kappname; i umjesto toga ćete morati koristiti ili "
"Liability ili Asset račun kako biste ručni vodili računa o svom kreditu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:601
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you omit one value &kappname; will try to calculate it for you. If you "
#| "have entered all values &kappname; will check the values are consistent. "
#| "&kappname; will not adjust entered values other than the \"Balloon payment"
#| "\", which it may adjust slightly to deal with rounding. If the values are "
#| "inconsistent or &kappname; cannot calculate the omitted value &kappname; "
#| "will let you know so that you can correct any errors and repeat the "
#| "calculation."
msgid ""
"If you omit one value, &kmymoney; will try to calculate it for you. If you "
"have entered all values &kmymoney; will check the values are consistent. "
"&kmymoney; will not adjust entered values other than the \"Balloon payment"
"\", which it may adjust slightly to deal with rounding. If the values are "
"inconsistent or &kmymoney; cannot calculate the omitted value, &kmymoney; "
"will let you know so that you can correct any errors and repeat the "
"calculation."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko izostavite samo jednu vrijednost &kappname; će pokušati da izvrši "
"proračun. Ukoliko ste unijeli sve vrijednosti &kappname; će provjeriti da li "
"su one sve konzistentne. &kappname; neće vršiti nikakvu promjenu unesenih "
"vrijednosti osim \"Balon isplate\", koju može neznatno promjeniti kako bi se "
"riješio problem oko zaokruživanja. Ukoliko vrijednosti nisu konzistentne ili "
"&kappname; ne može izračunati izostavljene vrijednosti, &kappname; će vas "
"obavijestiti kako bi mogli izvršiti korekciju eventualnih grešaka i ponoviti "
"proračun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:610
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Once the values are consistent the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button is "
#| "enabled and you can advance to the next page."
msgid ""
"Once the values are consistent, the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button is "
"enabled and you can advance to the next page."
msgstr ""
"Kada vrijednosti budu konzistentne, <guibutton>Sljedeći</guibutton> dugme će "
"biti omogućeno i moći ćete nastaviti na sljedeću stranicu."

